docs.title: Introduction
docs.description: High-performance CesiumJS providers for interactive 2D and 3D visualization of environmental and atmospheric data stored in Zarr.

docs.title: ZarrCubeProvider
docs.description: The ZarrCubeProvider renders 3D volumetric (cube) Zarr datasets as Cesium primitives.

docs.title: ZarrCubeVelocityProvider
docs.description: The ZarrCubeVelocityProvider loads and visualizes 3D vector fields (U, V components) from Zarr datasets as animated particle layers in Cesium using the WindLayer from cesium-wind-layer

docs.title: ZarrLayerProvider
docs.description: The ZarrLayerProvider allows you to render 2D raster data from Zarr datasets as a Cesium imagery layer.
